notes
CP-2 (or cp1) measurements coordinated with the German CHAMP satellite overpasses. The exact times may change depending on orbit changes. Part of German-Finnish campaign. Scanning is desired for a) measuring gravity waves and b) increasing      
chances of being conjugate to the CHAMP path.      

